This is a medium-level problem since $$O(n^2)$$ solution gets accepted. If the constraints were >= $$10^5$$, it would be hard.

My $$O(n^2)$$ solution:

```
class Solution {
public:
    int longestValidParentheses(string s) {
        int n = s.length(), res = 0;
        for(int i = 0; i < n; i++){
            int cnt = 0;
            for(int j = i; j < n; j++){
                if(!cnt and s[j] == ')') break;
                if(s[j] == '(') cnt++;
                else cnt--;
                if(!cnt) res = max(res, j - i + 1);
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
};
```

